{"tid":805673,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"影人地柯尿俾高層大佬見到","createTime":"2018-09-04T04:29:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-04T04:49:11.000Z","uid":9425,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5b1931670a375d6b0ae04d8a5ec7f7a90a703aa7","tid":805673,"uid":9425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T04:29:48.000Z","msg":"話說啱食完飯 梗係去公廁柯番督長命尿之後返去瞓下覺<br />\n咁我同我同事一齊去柯 隔壁有個呀叔急急步係我地隔離入去  點知入到去見到佢成隻狗嘅款柯尿笑撚到仆街<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/04/122927_7677c727da1606dd9a935e9e836a5551.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F04%2F122927_7677c727da1606dd9a935e9e836a5551.png&h=06c77798&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我就梗係拎出我手機影低佢 影其間突然有個熟悉身影喺隔壁<br />\n我一望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n柯完出去佢仲對住我同事陰陰咀笑<br />\n死啦 我嚟咗2個月咋 唔知會點諗我份人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0af8c65e329681b75d90cb31882f3dc573dea8e2","tid":805673,"uid":7332,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T04:31:50.000Z","msg":"On9 公廁影相犯法"},{"pid":"111d7ea59be56ff51f120134731ae07b22f89165","tid":805673,"uid":178658,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T04:33:13.000Z","msg":"樓主做清潔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf5858ebe97c2e14a98fc10cf8030b5641615262","tid":805673,"uid":9425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0af8c65e329681b75d90cb31882f3dc573dea8e2","tid":805673,"uid":7332,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T04:31:50.000Z","msg":"On9 公廁影相犯法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T04:33:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb31382249d2a3539c1952d3625dbdb9a1fc343c","tid":805673,"uid":21558,"like":6,"dislike